quran[58]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,Nditsuba khuinyanga yeyinduukho
  75,2,Ne nditsuba khu Mwoyo kwo khwifunaania
  75,3,Omundu aparanga mbu shikhulibusia halala ebikumba bibie tawe
  75,4,Khulwa shina! efwe khunyala okhura habwene tsinyali tsie tsinzala tsisie
  75,5,"Habula Omundu yenyangasa okhutsilila okhukhola amabii, khutsinyanga tsili imbeli waye"
  75,6,"Arebanga mbu: “iliba lina inyanga yeyindukho?”"
  75,7,Mana olwe Imoni iling’ang’aala
  75,8,Ne olwa Omwesi kulitilana
  75,9,Ne olwe Eliuba nende Omwesi bilihambasibwa
  75,10,"Inyanga eyo Omundu aliboola mbu: “amelushilo kali yena"
  75,11,"Tawe, okhwilushila abulaho"
  75,12,Inyanga eyo abulaho awundi wokhutsia halali wa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yenyene
  75,13,"Inyanga eyo\tOmundu aliboolelwa, kayaranjilila nende kayamalilikha"
  75,14,Halali buli Omundu amanyile omwoyo kukwe muno
  75,15,Kata nalarusia ebichila ebiinja
  75,16,"Olayungubasia\tulimi\tlulwo, khulwokhusooma lwangu lwangu tawe"
  75,17,Toto kalikhifwe okhubuusilia halala nende okhukhwibaalila
  75,18,"Nikhuyisooma, olondelele okhusooma khukhwe"
  75,19,Mana kali khwifwe okhukhwinoosilia
  75,20,"Shikali kario tawe, halali enywe mwayanza obulamu bwokhushialo"
  75,21,Ne mulekhanga obulamu bwomwikulu
  75,22,Obweni inyanga eyo bulimesamesa
  75,23,Buliheenga Nyasaye wabwo Omulesi
  75,24,Ne obweni inyanga eyo bulisinyikha
  75,25,"Bulimanya\tmbu\tbuulilwe\tnende shifunakanga olukongofuma"
  75,26,Shikali kario tawe! Lwo omwoyo kuliula khushikumba shielikosi
  75,27,"Mana kareebwe mbu:\t“ niwina umusilikha?”"
  75,28,Ne omwene namanya mbu toto bwene okho nikho okhufwa
  75,29,Ne olwa emiluku chilirebwa halala okundi khukundi
  75,30,Inyanga eyo niyokhuyililwakhwo awa Nyaseye wuwo Omulesi
  75,31,"Mana\tshiyafuchilila,\tnohomba shiyalaama tawe"
  75,32,Halali yakhaya nakalukhana
  75,33,Mana natsia khubandu baye niyesunga
  75,34,"Oh abaane koo ewe, oh abaane ko ewe"
  75,35,Mana khandi oh abaane koo ewe! Oh abaane koo ewe
  75,36,Mbu Omundu aparanga mbu alilekhwa butswa eshikhaya
  75,37,Shiyali indonyande yamatsi kolwibulo
  75,38,"Mana naba amalika, mana Nyasaye namuloonga namukaasia obulayi"
  75,39,"Mana namukhola tsimbia tsibili, abasatsa na bakhasi"
  75,40,"Kho\tkoo, oyo shali Omunyali wokhulamusia mubafu tawe"
  76,1,"Toto biabura ebise ebiinji khumundu, olwayalaali eshindu shilarumbulwa tawe"
  76,2,"Toto efwe khwaloonga Omundu okhurulana nende imwo yobulamu, yesasania, (yomusatsa nende omukhasi) khulwokhumutema, kho nikhumukhola wo khuwulila, nende wokhulola"
  76,3,"Toto efwe khwamwawulila injila, niyenya achame nohomba alobe"
  76,4,Toto efwe khwarecheshela Abakhayi eminyororo nende tsirimba nende omulilo omululu
  76,5,Toto Abandu abalayi balinywa eshinywebwa shiasasibwa mwo ‘kafura’
  76,6,"Ne Isebele ya Abandu ba Nyasaye balinywamwo, bali ikhola ikhulukusie mubunji"
  76,7,"Bakholanga kabalaka, ne baritsanga inyanga yobusiro bwayio buliswana"
  76,8,"Ne balisinjia eshilibwa, khulwo khuyanza khukhwe Abamanani, nende Abafwilwa nende Ababoye"
  76,9,Toto efwe khubalisinjia khulwokhwenya tsimbabasi tsia Nyasaye shikhubenyakhwo omurungo nohomba orio muno tawe
  76,10,"Toto efwe khuritsaanga okhurulana khu Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, inyanga yobutinyu nende Omusando"
  76,11,"Kho mana Nyasaye alibalinda , okhurulana khubusiro bwe inyanga eyo, ne alibabukanilia nomwikhoyo nende obusangafu"
  76,12,"Nealibarungaemikundachomwikulu nende tsingubo tsieshironyo, khulwa okhwifwila khwabu"
  76,13,"Omo baliyekha khubisaala bioluyali, shibalilolamwo omubasu omululu nohomba omunyiri omululu tawe"
  76,14,"Ne ebinikha biliba ahambi ninabo, ne – ebiamo- bilieletsanga okhuula hasi"
  76,15,Ne balitendelwa khubindu bie ifedha nende vikombe bie tsigilasi
  76,16,"Bieifedha inzwenufu shinga shiwoo, biachelwa khushichelo"
  76,17,"Ne omo balinywesibwamwo eshinywebwa\tshasasibwamwo itangawizi"
  76,18,Eyo ni Isebele iliyo ilangwa mbu Salsabil